{"about_the_game":"<strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Description</h2></strong><br>Crashy Laps is a game to enjoy driving and overtaking aggressively where collisions and foul play are common, with a maximum of 4 Players. 20 little and funny tracks are waiting for you.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257410/extras/animation_race.gif?t=1726465199\" /><br><br>In Single Player mode, you can also compete to reach the Best Time in the Leaderboard of each track.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257410/extras/animation_timetrial.gif?t=1726465199\" /><br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Features</h2></strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Use one or more <strong>Gamepads </strong>\ud83c\udfae, or <strong>Keyboard </strong>\u2328\ufe0f: you can use Keyboard for playing a maximum of 2 players at the same time.<br></li><li>4 Settings for each part of day: Morning, Midday \u2600, Evening \ud83c\udf04 and Night \ud83c\udf1b.<br></li><li>4 Competitions: Time Trial, Quick Race, Grand Prix and Championship.<br></li><li>4 Areas with their own settings: road grip, environment, terrain types, etc.<br></li><li>4 Tracks for each Area: <strong>16 Tracks + 4 Track variants.</strong><br></li><li>3 AI \ud83e\udd16 Difficulties: Novice, Professional and Expert.<br></li><li>2 selectable Camera Views: <strong>Isometric or Top-down</strong>. Zoom in or out to adjust screen for aspects ratio from 4:3 until 21:9.<br></li><li>2 selectable Engine Sounds: Combustion or Electric.<br></li><li><strong>Customization</strong>: customize the number and the car colours.</li></ul><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257410/extras/animation_customization_600px.gif?t=1726465199\" /><br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Competitions</h2></strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Time Trial \ud83c\udfce\ufe0f: play in Single Player mode and try to reach your Best Time and the World Record for each track.<br></li><li>Quick Race, from \ud83c\udfce\ufe0f\ud83c\udfce\ufe0f to \ud83c\udfce\ufe0f\ud83c\udfce\ufe0f\ud83c\udfce\ufe0f\ud83c\udfce\ufe0f: play a 4 laps race.<br></li><li>Grand Prix \ud83c\udfce\ufe0f\ud83c\udfce\ufe0f\ud83c\udfce\ufe0f\ud83c\udfce\ufe0f: play a Grand Prix with a qualifying lap for each player and 4 laps race.<br></li><li>Championship \ud83c\udfce\ufe0f\ud83c\udfce\ufe0f\ud83c\udfce\ufe0f\ud83c\udfce\ufe0f: play a Championship competing in the 4 Tracks of the selected Area and reach the Championship Cups by the selected difficulty.</li></ul><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Zones</h2></strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Candy Lands</strong>: drive in a sweet world where the mud is chocolate, on simple roads great for beginners.<br></li><li><strong>Alpine Bridge</strong>: drive in an alpine area, always crossing bridges and tunnels.<br></li><li><strong>Silver Dunes</strong>: drive in a desert area, on rough and uneven roads.<br></li><li><strong>Frosty Way</strong>: drive in an icy area surrounded by snowy mountains, on slippery and twisty roads.</li></ul><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257410/extras/animation_area_cl_150px.gif?t=1726465199\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257410/extras/animation_area_ab_150px.gif?t=1726465199\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257410/extras/animation_area_sd_150px.gif?t=1726465199\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257410/extras/animation_area_fw_150px.gif?t=1726465199\" /><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Around the World</strong>: drive in a tracks selection of the previous areas, with some changes.</li></ul><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akama